The paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as Optical Character Recognition (OCR), document level embedding, and Bidirectional Long Short-Term Memory (Bi-LSTM) for text classification. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
